Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

313
01:00:59,865 --> 01:01:03,077
Hey, Fuko!

314
01:01:03,160 --> 01:01:05,204
Fuko, what's wrong? Tell me.

315
01:01:05,287 --> 01:01:09,917
- I killed her! I killed Mom!
- Fuko!

316
01:01:10,084 --> 01:01:12,795
Fuko, get a grip!

317
01:01:13,253 --> 01:01:17,299
Mom killed herself! It wasn't your fault!

318
01:01:18,175 --> 01:01:19,385
You were small,

319
01:01:19,468 --> 01:01:21,887
