And Nagi, too.

331
01:02:36,545 --> 01:02:40,883
Let's have dinner. Nagi's waiting, too.

332
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:58,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
Yeah? What is it?

333
01:02:58,901 --> 01:02:59,985
No!

334
01:03:47,866 --> 01:03:52,704
You kill Sadako's child.

335
01:04:45,716 --> 01:04:47,593
Let's go home.

336
01:05:37,142 --> 01:05:39,353
Where are we going?

337
01:05:43,899 --> 01:05:45,400
Auntie?

338
01:08:10,921 --> 01:08:12,464
You'll kill me?

339
01:08:17,010 --> 01:08:19,012
You don't like me?

340
01:08:24,684 --> 01:08:27,521
Why's everyone scared of me?

341
01:08:32,567 --> 01:08:35,153
I want to see Mom.

342
01:08:41,993 --> 01:08:43,578
I'm so sorry...

343
01:08:43,954 --> 01:08:46,456
So sorry...

344
01:08:47,082 --> 01:08:48,875
- Sorry...
- I'm scared.

345
01:08:50,794 --> 01:08:53,713
I can see people's deaths.

346
01:08:55,006 --> 01:08:58,718
Help me, Auntie, help me...

347
01:09:23,910 --> 01:09:30,584
You know, we haven't spoken
like this in ages.

348
01:09:33,420 --> 01:09:38,091
When you're home, you avoid me.

349
01:09:40,302 --> 01:09:41,678
I'm busy.

350
01:09:41,761 --> 01:09:43,263
I need to go.

351
01:09:43,346 --> 01:09:45,557
Nagi needs your help.

352
01:09:52,647 --> 01:09:54,107
Nagi...

353
01:09:55,650 --> 01:09:56,526
She said so.

354
01:10:00,447 --> 01:10:01,907
Nagi...

355
01:10:03,575 --> 01:10:06,119
She may not be ordinary.

356
01:10:07,579 --> 01:10:13,251
But that's not what she wants.

357
01:10:17,005 --> 01:10:22,177
I... I want to help her.

358
01:10:27,265 --> 01:10:29,517
Tell me the truth.

359
01:10:31,311 --> 01:10:32,938
Is Nagi...

360
01:10:34,898 --> 01:10:37,067
...Sadako's child?

361
01:10:57,254 --> 01:10:58,797
Akane...

362
01:11:00,757 --> 01:11:02,259
She's alive.

363
01:12:54,746 --> 01:12:56,289
Five years ago,

364
01:12:56,956 --> 01:12:59,959
Sadako appeared before Akane and I.

365
01:13:01,961 --> 01:13:04,506
Akane has special powers.

366
01:13:06,216 --> 01:13:09,052
Sadako tried to use Akane's body

367
01:13:09,719 --> 01:13:11,388
to be born into this world.

368
01:13:14,099 --> 01:13:15,683
But Akane...

369
01:13:17,394 --> 01:13:20,688
She trapped Sadako in her body.

370
01:13:22,941 --> 01:13:24,317
Soon after,

371
01:13:25,402 --> 01:13:27,320
Akane got pregnant.

372
01:13:30,698 --> 01:13:32,826
That's Nagi?

373
01:13:35,120 --> 01:13:41,334
Akane is still fighting all alone.

374
01:13:46,464 --> 01:13:51,845
Nagi has been drawing Akane's picture.

375
01:14:01,855 --> 01:14:03,273
Nagi has...

376
01:14:05,275 --> 01:14:08,486
...always wanted to see her.

377
01:14:10,196 --> 01:14:11,739
Can't they meet?

378
01:14:12,615 --> 01:14:15,743
No, if Nagi sees Akane,

379
01:14:16,369 --> 01:14:18,663
Sadako will be resurrected.

380
01:14:18,788 --> 01:14:20,373
But that's...

381
01:14:21,458 --> 01:14:23,668
They had to be separated.

382
01:14:25,420 --> 01:14:30,383
That's why Akane...

383
01:14:30,884 --> 01:14:33,303
She has taken on everything
and stayed here.

384
01:14:36,890 --> 01:14:38,766
Akane has been...

385
01:14:40,477 --> 01:14:42,187
...preventing Sadako's power

386
01:14:42,270 --> 01:14:44,898
