390
01:14:54,699 --> 01:14:56,826
It's not Nagi.

391
01:14:59,662 --> 01:15:01,539
Then who?

392
01:15:47,210 --> 01:15:50,171
Nagi! Nagi's missing!

393
01:15:50,588 --> 01:15:52,423
Nagi's missing?

394
01:15:57,178 --> 01:15:58,137
Nagi...

395
01:16:01,140 --> 01:16:02,517
Takanori!

396
01:16:09,482 --> 01:16:10,316
Nagi...

397
01:16:23,788 --> 01:16:29,836
So... she is alive?
Akane Ayukawa.

398
01:16:30,962 --> 01:16:32,338
Don't move!

399
01:16:34,841 --> 01:16:36,175
Nagi...

400
01:16:50,857 --> 01:16:53,443
I'll kill them both.

401
01:16:54,235 --> 01:16:56,904
Somebody must end this!

402
01:16:59,407 --> 01:17:01,242
Nagi, run!

403
01:17:14,005 --> 01:17:16,257
Nagi, run!

